volume.name: Attack of the Zit Monster & Other Teenage Terrors
Attack of the Killer Tomatoes: The Comic

description: First missions. Eurystheus will send Hercule to the planet Nemea. On that tortured land a terrifying creature is attacking farms and decimating entire families. Hercule will have to hunt that vile beast, leaving behind the savagery and secrets that the Axiomatikos want to hide, at all costs, from the people they rule with an iron hand.
name: The Blood of Nemea
